PrecisAuthority to enter into a two-year AGREEMENT with the Province of Quebec and a one-year Agreement with each of the other provinces and territories which provide for the making of a financial contribution to offset costs incurred by them in the implementation of a comprehensive program for the VOCATIONAL REHABILITATION OF DISABLED PERSONS.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to enter into a two-year AGREEMENT with the Province of Quebec
and a one-year Agreement with each of the other provinces and territories
which provide for the making of a financial contribution to offset costs
incurred by them in the implementation of a comprehensive program for the
VOCATIONAL REHABILITATION OF DISABLED PERSONS.
